The Addams Family;;66;;65;;PG-13;;When a man (Christopher Lloyd) claiming to be Fester, the missing brother of Gomez Addams (Raul Julia), arrives at the Addams' home, the family is thrilled. However, Morticia (Anjelica Huston) begins to suspect the man is a fraud, since he cannot recall details of Fester's life. With the help of lawyer Tully Alford (Dan Hedaya), Fester manages to get the Addams clan evicted from their home. Gomez realizes the two men are conspiring to swindle the Addams fortune and that he must challenge Fester.;;Comedy;;Barry Sonnenfeld;;1991;;Anjelica Huston,Raul Julia,Christopher Lloyd,Dan Hedaya,Elizabeth Wilson,Judith Malina,Carel Struycken,Dana Ivey,Paul Benedict,Christina Ricci,Jimmy Workman,Christopher Hart,John Franklin;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/addams_family